steps.name: Authorize user with valid email admin@gmail.com and password admin
Click on guest dropdown
Click on `Увійти` button
Set values 'admin@gmail.com'/'admin' for `Емейл` and `Пароль` fields
Fill in Password field: 'admin'
Click on Submit button
Click on dropdown for authorized user in top right corner of header
Click on 'Мій профіль' button in dropdown for authorized users
Click on 'Додати' button
Click on 'Додати гурток' button
Enter ValidName2 data into the 'Назва' field of 'Основна інформація' tab
Check off 'Спортивні секції' check-box from 'Категорія' group box
Enter 2 into the first age input and 18 in second age input
Click on 'Наступний крок' button
Click the 'Додати локацію' link on the 'Контакти' tab
Checking that 'Додати локацію' pop-up is opened
Enter data into the 'Назва' field of 'Додати локацію' pop-up
Check if data for the field with Id name is accepted
Click on 'Місто' dropdown
Choose a 'Київ' city from the 'Місто' drop-down list
Check if data for the field with Id cityName is accepted
Click on 'Метро/Місцевість' dropdown
Choose a 'Академмістечко' locality from the 'Метро/Міцевість' drop-down list
Check if data for the field with Id stationName is accepted
Click on 'Район міста' dropdown
Choose a 'Деснянський' district from the 'Місто' drop-down list
Check if data for the field with Id districtName is accepted
Enter data ValidAddress into the 'Адреса' field
Check if data for the field with Id address is accepted
Enter data 49.829104498711104, 24.005058710351314 into the 'Географічні координати' field
Check if data for the field with Id coordinates is accepted
Enter data 0966666666 into the 'Номер телефону' field
Check if data for the field with Id phone is accepted
Click the 'Додати' button
Enter 0966666666 data into Phone number field of 'Контакти' area
Check if data for the field with Id basic_contactТелефон is accepted
Enter ValidName2 data into Facebook field of 'Контакти' area
Check if data for the field with Id basic_contactFacebook is accepted
Enter ValidName2 data into WhatsApp field of 'Контакти' area
Check if data for the field with Id basic_contactWhatsApp is accepted
Enter example@email.com data into Email field of 'Контакти' area
Check if data for the field with Id basic_contactПошта is accepted
Enter ValidName2 data into Skype field of 'Контакти' area
Check if data for the field with Id basic_contactSkype is accepted
Enter ValidName2 data into Site field of 'Контакти' area
Check if data for the field with Id basic_contactContact is accepted
Click on 'Наступний крок' button

Fill 'Опис' field with Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
